      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/concept-a-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "两段直线在原点恰好接上，图像是一个漂亮的 V 字。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "piecewise-function",
      "section_id": "concept-b",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "concept-b-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/concept-b-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "判断分段点连不连续，关键看曲线在那里断没断开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "piecewise-function",
      "section_id": "concept-b",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "concept-b-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/concept-b-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "符号函数在原点两侧一个负一一个正一，接不上，就是跳跃间断。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "piecewise-function",
      "section_id": "concept-c",
      "line_id": "lim-2",
      "filename": "concept-c-lim-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/concept-c-lim-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "左右极限相等且等于函数值，就连续；不相等，就出现跳跃。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "piecewise-function",
      "section_id": "concept-c",
      "line_id": "lim-3",
      "filename": "concept-c-lim-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/concept-c-lim-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "实心点表示真正取到的值，空心圈表示极限逼近但取不到。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "piecewise-function",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "切换不同例子，观察取整函数一级一级往上跳的阶梯。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "piecewise-function",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/piecewise-function/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "比较分段点的左右极限，就能判断它连续还是跳跃间断。"
    },
